OL,3,CSecrets of gold discovered in a series
OL,4,Cof 'ground-breaking' experiments
OL,6,FSome of the secrets of gold have been
OL,7,Funcovered by a team of scientists led
OL,8,Fby a Belfast university.
OL,10,FThe team conducted a series of "ground-
OL,11,Fbreaking" experiments on the precious
OL,12,Fmetal and its melting point.
OL,14,FThe metal was found to react
OL,15,Funexpectedly to extreme temperatures.
OL,17,FThe scientists used high-intensity
OL,18,Flasers to heat gold to very high
OL,19,Ftemperatures and observe the results
OL,20,Fat the atomic level.
