OL,3,CSecrets of gold discovered in a series
OL,4,Cof 'ground-breaking' experiments
OL,6,FContrary to expectations, the metal
OL,7,Fstopped melting and instead became
OL,8,Fharder and stronger past a certain
OL,9,Fheat threshold.
OL,11,FEver-increasing amounts of energy
OL,12,F(heat) were then required to bring the
OL,13,Fgold to melting point.
OL,15,FThe lasers used are called femtosecond
OL,16,Flasers and operate on ultrafast
OL,17,Ftimescales, with a femtosecond being
OL,18,Fone millionth of a billionth of a
OL,19,Fsecond.
