OL,3,CSecrets of gold discovered in a series
OL,4,Cof 'ground-breaking' experiments
OL,6,FThe scientists followed up the laser
OL,7,Fhits by observing the changes using
OL,8,Ffemtosecond-duration X-ray pulses.
OL,10,FThese experiments were carried out
OL,11,Fusing the highest-resolution X-ray
OL,12,Fmachines available in the world. Only
OL,13,Ffive research facilities exist
OL,14,Fglobally with this kind of equipment
OL,15,Fand top researchers must compete for
OL,16,Fhighly prized and restricted timeslots.
OL,18,FThe discovery is set to have wide-
OL,19,Franging implications for technology
OL,20,Fand industry.
