OL,3,CSecrets of gold discovered in a series
OL,4,Cof 'ground-breaking' experiments
OL,6,FDr Adrien Descamps and Dr Emma
OL,7,FMcBride, from the Queen's University
OL,8,FBelfast, led a team from the UK, US,
OL,9,FGermany and France, at the Linac
OL,10,FCoherent Light Source, an X-ray Free
OL,11,FElectron Laser at the SLAC National
OL,12,FAccelerator Laboratory in California.
OL,14,FDr Descamps described the study as a
OL,15,F"bridge between theoretical physics
OL,16,Fand the real world".
