OL,3,CSecrets of gold discovered in a series
OL,4,Cof 'ground-breaking' experiments
OL,6,FHe said: "And while the simulations of
OL,7,Fthe past may have posited that this
OL,8,Feffect might be possible, our
OL,9,Fexperiment has provided hundreds of
OL,10,Fdata points, giving an enormous amount
OL,11,Fof detail and evidence which was
OL,12,Fpreviously unavailable.
OL,14,F"You can only get this kind of detail
OL,15,Fat the atomic level ` we were probing
OL,16,Fthe timescale between before applying
OL,17,Fthe laser and the material blowing up
OL,18,F` which is a tiny fraction of a split-
OL,19,Fsecond.
