OL,6,F"You can only really study that at
OL,7,Fpico-second scale ` it happens too
OL,8,Ffast to see with the naked eye or in
OL,9,F'real time'."
OL,11,FDr McBride added: "It was such a
OL,12,Fprivilege to use these highly
OL,13,Fspecialised and expensive X-Ray
OL,14,Fmachines and we are amazingly grateful
OL,15,Ffor that opportunity.
