OL,3,CSecrets of gold discovered in a series
OL,4,Cof 'ground-breaking' experiments
OL,6,F"We wouldn't have been able to carry
OL,7,Fout this experiment more than 10 years
OL,8,Fago ` this kind of sophisticated
OL,9,Fmachinery simply didn't exist, and we
OL,10,Fhad no way of knowing how materials
OL,11,Fwould respond to lasers at such
OL,12,Fintensity.
OL,14,F"By proving that phonon hardening is
OL,15,Findeed real and can be evidenced, it
OL,16,Fwill increase our understanding of how
OL,17,Fenergy flows and how materials
OL,18,Frespond. This will be invaluable for
OL,19,Fthe future of applied science and
OL,20,Ftechnology."
